    GIT Workflow
- git branch 'branch_name'          # create branch
- git checkout 'branch_name'        # switch current workspace to branch
- work, work, work!
- git commit -a -m "Something"      # commit changes to branch
- git checkout master               # switch to master 
- git merge                         # merge changes back to master
- git branch -d 'branch_name'       # clean up merged branches

